Usage: gui_deselect [-help] {-all  | -rect {x1 y1 x2 y2} | -point {x y} | -line {x1 y1 x2 y2}}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-all                    # Deselect all objects (bool, optional)
-line {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Deselect by line (box, optional)
-point {x y}            # Deselect by point (point, optional)
-rect {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Deselect by box (box, optional)